17:
The following Levites rebuilt the next several sections of the wall:
Rehum son of Bani built the next section;
Hashabiah, ruler of half the Keilah District, built the next section on behalf of his district;

13:
At Mount Sinai you came down from heaven;
you spoke to your people
and gave them good laws and sound teachings.

35:
With your blessing, kings ruled your people
when they lived in the broad, fertile land you gave them;
but they failed to turn from sin and serve you.
